 civil servants running education are Sadtu members", claimed the international news source.On Wednesday, South Africa&rsquo;s basic education department reported a matriculation pass rate - including progressed students - of 72.5%. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.